@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
[*] --> OnHold
OnHold --> Closed : cancel
Closed --> Cancelled : update
Closed : entry / log amenity
Cancelled --> Completed : confirm
Cancelled : entry / log amenity
Completed --> Pending : approve
Pending --> Created : reject
Created --> Closed : revert
Created --> [*]
@enduml